{"about_the_game":"Greedventory is a gorgeous pixel-art linear action RPG experience, where the only thing standing between you and an embarrassingly swift death is your mouse. Strike, parry, and cast powerful spells on your enemies, loot increasingly magnificent treasures and equipment, get lost in a beautifully brutal world, take down a centuries old not-so-secret society, and become the hero you REALLY don\u2019t want to be!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1895820/extras/Greedventory1_600x200.gif?t=1729084073\" /><br><br>In a world where magical artifacts are common, an ancient brotherhood rules and strives to collect and hoard every facet of ancient magic. The main rule of survival here is to always be aware of your surroundings and keep your reflexes in tip-top shape, as the realm runs on GREED, and no mortal being can resist the urge to steal, lie, and throw you to the wolves if it means THEY get something for YOUR trouble.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1895820/extras/Greedventory2_600x200.gif?t=1729084073\" /><br><br>Put your reflexes to the test in a reactive combat system, where every move is made with your cursor, every precious second counts, and quick reaction is the key to not getting blown up or cut into pieces!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1895820/extras/Greedventory3_600x200.gif?t=1729084073\" /><br><br>Explore every inch of a masterfully and passionately crafted pixel-art world chock full of magic, secrets, GREED, and <i>very</i> sassy humor! Collect practical, yet absolutely <i>DASHING</i> armor, deadly weapons, and if that isn\u2019t enough, imbue them with ancient magic to bestow special abilities, mix and match magical powers to maximize their potential!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1895820/extras/Greedventory4_600x200.gif?t=1729084073\" /><br><br>Live (or die) through a brutal story of deception and fraud, where even the friendliest looking fella is looking to rob you, be smart, and learn to use their weapons against them!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1895820/extras/Greedventory5_600x200.gif?t=1729084073\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"High Ambitions","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1895820/91a0582641351c5c67e8e3e78f2f03b515fcbf70.jpg"},{"name":"Sleight of Hand","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1895820/473eb406edaefa83dc0526ebbcd62105f9fbe9f3.jpg"},{"name":"Reverse Polarity","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1895820/efea9b46bdf39ff90cea481133c4246c4b0bb0b7.jpg"},{"name":"Spider Bender","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1895820/04f5e2bb003cfd0aa567054714fff436e7ff37b8.jpg"},{"name":"Master of Origami","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1895820/d8d11093e5689979de6f8ffc255fd3f0e2ca640d.jpg"},{"name":"So long, Sucker!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1895820/23344e649258f6c0bd9b60e7b6a8c73f48b8ca10.jpg"},{"name":"Broken Collar","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1895820/ffe0f778232d302b0c24238611dee59fff6f9e02.jpg"},{"name":"Why Not on Eagles Though","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1895820/c6385c95da2a1effb5919031f3548eaec6b1d904.jpg"},{"name":"A Final Say","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1895820/eeeb90a322870ad1ba689d47ce81d54b0dafc053.jpg"},{"name":"Aye, captain!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1895820/42bca40fc